name: The power and beauty of nature

metadata.name: Thunderstorm
metadata.description:
I decided to draw the first picture from the collection that I like the most. Namely, the sea and the storm. I think they're just made for each other.

The painting is painted in oil on canvas.
Canvas size 46x55 cm
The creation time is 1.5 months.
